Welcome to Unleash Your Potential! UofGH Leadership Conference 2024! Get ready to be inspired, motivated, and empowered to reach your full potential.

Join us in person starting on Saturday, September 7, 2024, from 8:45 am- 4:00 pm for a day filled with engaging speakers, interactive workshops, and networking opportunities.

Whether you're a first-year student looking to kickstart your university life, or an experienced leader seeking fresh perspectives, this conference is for you. Learn from industry experts, connect with like-minded individuals, and discover the leader within you.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to unleash your potential and take your leadership skills to the next level. Mark your calendars and get ready for a transformative experience at the UofGH Leadership Conference 2024!

For more information on the conference schedule and FAQs, please visit: https://www.guelphhumber.ca/life/get-involved

The UofGH Alumni Services team invite you and your family to our first-ever UofGH Alumni & Family BBQ!

Join us at this drop-in event for a BBQ lunch and ice cream, picnic games, kids activities, family photo opportunity, giveaways and prizes and MORE.

If you are interested in the family photo opportunity, please select that option when you register. We will reach out to you within the coming weeks to book your session time.

Limited space available so register today! Registration will close on August 2. We canâ€™t wait to see you there.

Before you begin classes in September, chat with our Academic Advisors live to discuss your plan for academic success and transfer credits.

We highly recommend that you attend this event where you will be provided essential information that will help you to prepare for your upcoming semester at the University of Guelph-Humber.
